  "keyFeatures": [
    "Go REST API with chi router and PostgreSQL (pgx/sqlc)",
    "React 19 + TypeScript frontend with Tailwind CSS and shadcn/ui",
    "Payment CRUD — list, get by ID, and create payments",
    "Docker Compose for local development with live-reload (Air)",
